Program: Omnibus
Title: Yoga Head to Toe
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m36
Last Broadcast Date: 15 November 2000
‘How long are you going to stand on your head for?’ An interview with Iyengar, the founder of "Iyengar Yoga" who is considered one of the foremost yoga teachers in the world. Contributors include Diana Clifton.